minar in the online edition of the world journal are available on the southeast asia forum website beyond representation portrayals of an overseas chinese tycoon in southeast asia rethinking the overseas chinese what's in a name world journal huang jianli suggests the term overseas chinese chinese language search seaf news of interest china's frown diplomacy in southeast asia donald k emmerson asia times on october 5 2010 visiting scholar's research on southeast asia published and forthcoming in japan december 16 2008 news applications from mid career and senior southeast asianist scholars for the 2008 2009 lee kong chian nus stanford distinguished fellowship on southeast asia december 20 2007 shorenstein aparc announcement shorenstein aparc is pleased to announce the lee kong chian nus stanford initiative on southeast asia october 18 2007 shorenstein aparc news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 725 2429 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
